---
name: head-field-box
---

# helper: a case class whose SECOND field is named `head`

Mirrors busi's `RepoRef(name, head)` (core/repo_commit.ssc) — the shape that
poisoned `List.head` dispatch on the v2 VM.

```scalascript
case class Ref(name: String, head: String)

def mkRef(n: String, h: String): Ref = Ref(n, h)
```
